column4: NSLOCTEXT("[0BC82758436EF51C3B48D785480FCE66]", "44E706254E9A2168AE999BA64FB377C0", "Are you having trouble because you\'ve got too much stuff?")
NSLOCTEXT("[0BC82758436EF51C3B48D785480FCE66]", "560C696E44541064107FC9B241C02FF2", "There is a place to find a key chain that connects your bag to another dimension.")
NSLOCTEXT("[0BC82758436EF51C3B48D785480FCE66]", "5BA14C1E4A55F308B86732B328AFD67E", "It increases the number of Items you can carry.")
NSLOCTEXT("[0BC82758436EF51C3B48D785480FCE66]", "F8933F014B486CF4ADD926BB690BFB1E", "Even if you\'ve been to some place before, look again.")
NSLOCTEXT("[0BC82758436EF51C3B48D785480FCE66]", "6C41D8CF470A44368593089BF387C056", "I\'ll tell you the secret to Item buying.")
NSLOCTEXT("[0BC82758436EF51C3B48D785480FCE66]", "D9740F78453130AD5DA3D9B1F4A3333B", "Press the Start button on the Item you want to get information for!")
NSLOCTEXT("[0BC82758436EF51C3B48D785480FCE66]", "BD5E07F44BAE5209F83D849BBFEBDC2B", "Choose the Item with [E], and press [UP], if you want to buy a lot.")
NSLOCTEXT("[0BC82758436EF51C3B48D785480FCE66]", "4F0185BA4D93ADA32E6EC99C3ABE9CE3", "To raise or lower by ten, use Up or Down on Dir. Pad, while pressing")
NSLOCTEXT("[0BC82758436EF51C3B48D785480FCE66]", "6A0C0177407F86DEDB8C0EBB5AD71E26", "Oh, right after digivolution, try buying something. Something good should happen!")
